00:20.450 --> 00:24.670
<b>Boys' National
Soccer Tournament
Itoshi Sae</b>

00:21.270 --> 00:24.050
<b><i>He's super amazing.</i></b>

00:24.930 --> 00:30.110
<b>So, Itoshi Sae-kun, how does it feel to have 
the world watching you as a soccer prodigy?</b>

00:31.530 --> 00:33.340
<b>What kind of player do you want to be?</b>

00:33.340 --> 00:36.370
<b>Whatever. Shut up. 
It's none of your business.</b>

00:36.370 --> 00:37.720
<b>Huh? Hey...</b>

00:38.040 --> 00:39.200
<b>Let's go home, Rin.</b>

00:39.510 --> 00:40.470
<b>Okay.</b>

00:40.470 --> 00:43.940
<b>H-He already has the 
charisma of a superstar.</b>

00:43.940 --> 00:49.610
<b>L-Let's move on. Here's the replay
 of Sae-kun's super play.</b>

00:50.440 --> 00:53.570
<b><i>Big Bro's kinda funny.</i></b>

00:57.100 --> 00:59.990
<b>I won. How about you?</b>

00:58.140 --> 00:58.790
<b>You
Win</b>

00:58.790 --> 00:59.210
<b>You
Win</b>

00:59.210 --> 00:59.580
<b>You
Win</b>

