<b>You
Lose</b>

01:00.790 --> 01:01.170
<b>You
Lose</b>

01:01.170 --> 01:01.580
<b>You
Lose</b>

01:01.580 --> 01:01.710
<b>You
Lose</b>

01:03.070 --> 01:03.810
<b>Hmph.</b>

01:04.400 --> 01:08.350
<b>Anyone who uses up their luck on stuff 
like this will never be the best in the world.</b>

01:08.730 --> 01:11.420
<b>Really? Is that how luck works?</b>

01:11.970 --> 01:14.430
<b>I'll become the best striker in the world.</b>

01:14.790 --> 01:16.500
<b>Everything else is meaningless.</b>

01:16.860 --> 01:18.390
<b>Huh.</b>

01:19.280 --> 01:22.480
<b><i>Big Bro really hates losing.</i></b>

01:28.450 --> 01:29.710
<b>Other side! Other side!</b>

01:29.710 --> 01:31.520
<b>Mark Itoshi Sae!</b>

01:32.170 --> 01:34.490
<b><i>Big Bro won't lose to anyone.</i></b>

01:36.300 --> 01:37.430
<b><i>And I...</i></b>

01:39.530 --> 01:43.160
<b><i>I also want to...</i></b>

01:44.350 --> 01:48.000
<b><i>I wanna be strong and cool like my big bro.</i></b>

01:58.610 --> 01:59.300
<b><i>Rin.</i></b>

02:03.370 --> 02:06.770
<b><i>Can I be the best striker
 in the world, too?</i></b>

02:11.950 --> 02:14.360
<b>Hey, what's this runt doing on the field?</b>

02:14.710 --> 02:15.450
<b>Move.</b>

02:16.070 --> 02:18.490
<b>Sorry, Big Bro. I...</b>

02:20.780 --> 02:22.180
<b>That was awesome, Rin.</b>

02:22.570 --> 02:24.200
<b>Play soccer with me.</b>

02:24.570 --> 02:25.460
<b>Huh?</b>

02:26.960 --> 02:30.500
<b>You can be the second 
strongest player after me.</b>

02:31.580 --> 02:32.390
<b>Right.</b>

02:33.450 --> 02:37.130
<b><i>I have the kindest big brother in the world.</i></b>

04:09.520 --> 04:09.560
<b>Episode</b>

04:09.610 --> 04:13.030
<b>Episode</b>

04:10.150 --> 04:13.020
<b>Night Snow</b>

04:14.010 --> 04:15.020
<b>Wow.</b>

04:15.360 --> 04:17.650
<b>Can you believe this, dear?</b>

04:17.650 --> 04:20.750
<b>Isagi Yoichi's Mother</b>

04:18.060 --> 04:21.400
<b>It's incredible that Yocchan
made the starting lineup,</b>

04:21.400 --> 04:22.990
<b>and his team is winning.</b>

04:22.990 --> 04:25.880
<b>Isagi Yoichi's Father</b>

04:23.210 --> 04:27.320
<b>I know zilch about soccer, 
but I'm already happy.</b>

04:29.070 --> 04:31.310
<b>What do you think you're doing, Meguru?!</b>

04:31.310 --> 04:33.290
<b>You've gotta go for the goal!</b>

04:33.630 --> 04:36.250
<b>You call yourself a striker?!</b>

04:36.250 --> 04:41.010
<b>Bachira Meguru's Mother</b>

04:36.900 --> 04:40.560
<b>Oh, I'm sorry. My son's playing.</b>

04:41.010 --> 04:43.130
<b>Oh, ours is too!</b>

04:43.130 --> 04:45.050
<b>Our son is No. 11.</b>

04:45.050 --> 04:48.800
<b>Really? On the same team? 
My son's No. 8.</b>

04:48.800 --> 04:50.630
<b>Oh, gosh!</b>

04:50.630 --> 04:52.600
<b>Let's shake hands!</b>

04:52.850 --> 04:56.230
<b>Thank you. I appreciate your son 
playing soccer with mine.</b>

04:56.230 --> 04:57.210
<b>Huh?</b>

04:57.210 --> 05:00.190
<b>I don't think I've ever seen my son...</b>

05:02.250 --> 05:05.110
<b>looking so happy to be playing soccer.</b>

05:06.120 --> 05:07.690
<b>The pleasure is all ours.</b>

05:07.690 --> 05:10.830
<b>Thank you for your support and care.</b>

05:11.190 --> 05:12.340
<b>Hyoma!</b>

05:13.570 --> 05:15.340
<b>Over here, Hyoma!</b>

05:15.340 --> 05:16.040
<b><i>Bah.</i></b>

05:16.040 --> 05:18.750
<b>Oh, he saw us, Mom.</b>

05:19.020 --> 05:21.520
<b>Hey, who's the cutie?</b>

05:21.520 --> 05:22.570
<b>My big sis.</b>

05:22.570 --> 05:25.020
<b>Not BON. Yer good-lookin' siblings.</b>

05:25.020 --> 05:26.800
<b><i>Bah, this is so embarrassing.</i></b>

05:27.400 --> 05:30.800
<b>Hyoma's beaming again,
 just like he used to.</b>

05:30.800 --> 05:34.450
<b>Yeah. He's finally back.</b>

05:35.930 --> 05:38.810
<b>What's going on, Mr. Manager?!</b>

05:38.870 --> 05:42.170
<b>U-20 Manager</b>

05:39.440 --> 05:42.960
<b>Do you understand 
the meaning of this match?!</b>

05:43.400 --> 05:47.610
<b>Japan Football Union
Special Adviser</b>

05:46.010 --> 05:47.610
<b>O-Of course.</b>

05:47.610 --> 05:52.580
<b>But contrary to our expectations, 
th-the other team is, well...</b>

05:52.800 --> 05:56.600
<b>Winners are always right.
Losers are always wrong.</b>

05:56.600 --> 05:58.920
<b>I don't need excuses.</b>

06:02.710 --> 06:07.050
<b>Hoicchan, I don't care what you have to do.</b>

06:07.630 --> 06:13.600
<b>We <i>must</i> win today to become
 the righteous of Japanese soccer!</b>

06:15.910 --> 06:18.880
<b>Results are everything in sports.</b>

06:19.370 --> 06:21.720
<b>Crush Blue Lock.</b>

06:23.700 --> 06:25.320
<b>Hell yeah!</b>

06:25.320 --> 06:27.490
<b>We can win this! We're the bomb, guys!</b>

06:27.490 --> 06:28.880
<b>Did you see?</b>

06:28.880 --> 06:33.310
<b>My glam clearance with 
that desperate spinning kick?</b>

06:34.520 --> 06:35.590
<b>Outta my face!</b>

06:37.780 --> 06:40.000
<b>Nice sprintin', Chigiri-kun.</b>

06:40.330 --> 06:41.500
<b>How're the legs?</b>

06:41.860 --> 06:43.320
<b>Thanks, Hiori.</b>

06:43.630 --> 06:45.850
<b>Yeah, I can still run.</b>

06:46.500 --> 06:48.170
<b>Towel, towel...</b>

06:50.800 --> 06:51.980
<b>Here you go, Nagi.</b>

06:52.360 --> 06:53.470
<b>Nice goal.</b>

06:54.250 --> 06:55.790
<b>But you can score more, right?</b>

06:56.270 --> 06:57.470
<b>I know you can.</b>

06:57.770 --> 06:58.910
<b>Yeah, Reo.</b>

06:59.530 --> 07:00.740
<b>I can keep it up.</b>

07:03.750 --> 07:06.360
<b>Everyone, great work in the first half.</b>

07:06.360 --> 07:07.930
<b>Thanks.</b>

07:07.930 --> 07:11.200
<b>Pipe down, diamonds in the rough.</b>

07:11.200 --> 07:13.830
<b>Let's recap that first half.</b>

07:13.830 --> 07:16.300
<b>How did you manage to score those goals?</b>

07:16.300 --> 07:20.680
<b>You need to carve into your brains 
the mechanics of what's happened so far.</b>

07:21.410 --> 07:24.710
<b>We had plans going into this game.</b>

07:24.710 --> 07:27.690
<b>But they initially didn't work.</b>

07:28.340 --> 07:32.220
<b>The one who made the breakthrough 
was undoubtedly Itoshi Rin.</b>

07:32.520 --> 07:34.980
<b>Helped by Isagi Yoichi.</b>

07:35.820 --> 07:37.940
<b>By playing closer together
 than we trained,</b>

07:37.940 --> 07:40.550
<b>and by having Isagi Yoichi 
around you at all times,</b>

07:40.550 --> 07:43.480
<b>you significantly increased your options.</b>

07:44.110 --> 07:47.020
<b>Itoshi Rin, why did you do that?</b>

07:47.450 --> 07:52.250
<b>To get past their four-man defense, 
I needed a sacrifice.</b>

07:52.760 --> 07:55.160
<b>Isagi happened to fit the role easily.</b>

07:55.160 --> 07:56.870
<b>"Sacrifice," huh?</b>

07:57.180 --> 07:58.580
<b>I like that answer.</b>

07:59.030 --> 08:01.620
<b>Such things don't happen
 on the training field.</b>

08:02.070 --> 08:06.590
<b>In fact, Isagi Yoichi, do you 
think of yourself as a sacrifice?</b>

08:06.820 --> 08:09.670
<b>No. I'm gonna score a goal myself.</b>

08:09.670 --> 08:12.130
<b>Right. That's how you should feel.</b>

08:12.810 --> 08:15.350
<b>All eleven of you out on that field</b>

08:15.350 --> 08:20.560
<b>have egos telling you that you're playing 
the lead role and you must fight this battle.</b>

08:21.390 --> 08:24.570
<b>That's what has got us here.</b>

08:22.110 --> 08:24.570
<b>The JFU presents</b>

08:22.110 --> 08:24.570
<b>Japan's U-20s vs. Blue Lock</b>

08:22.110 --> 08:24.570
<b>First Half 
Over</b>

08:24.970 --> 08:28.730
<b>However, that doesn't mean 
the second half will go the same way.</b>

08:28.730 --> 08:31.420
<b>Or rather, we <i>know</i> it won't.</b>

08:31.780 --> 08:35.860
<b>So stop celebrating and getting 
carried away right this second.</b>

08:37.000 --> 08:39.920
<b>You've achieved nothing yet.</b>

08:41.130 --> 08:44.080
<b>Don't be satisfied. Keep on attacking.</b>

08:44.490 --> 08:49.180
<b>Refuse to relinquish your right to be 
in the lead role until the very last second.</b>

08:50.010 --> 08:50.830
<b>That's all.</b>

08:51.430 --> 08:53.130
<b>We won't change formation.</b>

08:54.990 --> 08:57.260
<b>I only have one instruction 
for the second half.</b>

08:58.000 --> 08:59.500
<b>Make it a rout.</b>

09:01.130 --> 09:02.260
<b><i>That's right.</i></b>

09:02.650 --> 09:06.560
<b><i>We're not playing this 
just so we can win together.</i></b>

09:07.130 --> 09:09.540
<b><i>I need to keep battling for my own goals.</i></b>

09:10.030 --> 09:12.780
<b><i>And just like how he's doing it his way...</i></b>

09:13.910 --> 09:17.120
<b><i>I will prove myself in this game.</i></b>

09:18.490 --> 09:21.940
<b>Crap, crap, crap.</b>

09:21.940 --> 09:24.200
<b>Never thought we'd let 'em take the lead.</b>

09:24.530 --> 09:26.540
<b>What are we gonna do in the second half?</b>

09:27.130 --> 09:28.920
<b>If only I'd scored...</b>

09:29.820 --> 09:32.250
<b>Perfect timing, Genius.</b>

09:32.250 --> 09:34.510
<b>We're discussing changes
 for the second half.</b>

09:34.510 --> 09:37.760
<b>That last attack in 
the first half almost came off.</b>

09:37.760 --> 09:40.300
<b>They'll freak out if we commit
 more men to the attack.</b>

09:40.860 --> 09:42.850
<b>Should we request a tweak of formation?</b>

09:42.850 --> 09:45.240
<b>Huh? Do what you like.</b>

09:45.240 --> 09:46.730
<b>It's not my problem anymore.</b>

09:46.730 --> 09:49.440
<b>Huh? What are you talking about?</b>

09:51.690 --> 09:52.890
<b>I'm leaving.</b>

09:53.400 --> 09:55.850
<b>Huh? What do you mean by <i>that</i>?!</b>

09:55.850 --> 09:58.250
<b>Without you, there's no game.</b>

09:58.250 --> 10:00.030
<b>He's moisturizing his face?</b>

10:00.030 --> 10:04.630
<b>I don't care. Those were the terms of 
the bet with your captain over there.</b>

10:05.250 --> 10:07.080
<b>A bet with Aiku?</b>

10:07.130 --> 10:10.130
<b>Let us win without Shidou.</b>

10:10.170 --> 10:12.590
<b>I'll be the one testing you.</b>

10:12.850 --> 10:16.640
<b>If you can't keep up with me, I'm out.</b>

10:17.650 --> 10:20.820
<b>You're a useless, defective bunch.</b>

10:20.820 --> 10:22.430
<b>That's the reality.</b>

10:23.070 --> 10:27.460
<b>Still, I only came here because 
I was interested in Blue Lock.</b>

10:28.680 --> 10:31.020
<b>They're still crude,</b>

10:31.020 --> 10:35.120
<b>but it's clear what they're seeing and 
aiming for is totally different from you.</b>

10:36.520 --> 10:39.130
<b>That's all I needed to know.</b>

10:40.370 --> 10:42.870
<b>I have no reason to stay here any longer.</b>

10:44.200 --> 10:46.210
<b>Hold on, Li'l Genius.</b>

10:47.790 --> 10:51.230
<b>Sorry, guys. I made a very selfish bet.</b>

10:51.990 --> 10:55.670
<b>I wanted to test the skills we have now.</b>

10:56.520 --> 11:00.380
<b>And I wanted to see where I stood.</b>

11:01.340 --> 11:03.560
<b>But it's painfully clear now.</b>

11:04.410 --> 11:05.390
<b>We are...</b>

11:06.600 --> 11:07.620
<b>weak.</b>

11:11.050 --> 11:17.900
<b>At this rate, the U-20s will be taken over, 
and we'll be the ones who disappear.</b>

11:20.380 --> 11:25.150
<b>It burns and stings worse than 
I've ever felt in my whole life.</b>

11:25.740 --> 11:28.300
<b>Too late for you to notice that now.</b>

11:28.640 --> 11:31.460
<b>With me leaving, 
this team has no chance of winning.</b>

11:31.920 --> 11:34.210
<b>Oh, but we do.</b>

11:35.170 --> 11:36.980
<b>We still have that devil.</b>

11:37.920 --> 11:40.030
<b>Hey, genius.</b>

11:40.030 --> 11:44.640
<b>Isn't the life form known as yours truly
reason enough for you to stay?</b>

11:46.010 --> 11:48.550
<b>Was that your play all along?</b>

11:52.660 --> 11:54.710
<b>Go berserk, Devil Boy.</b>

11:55.290 --> 11:58.400
<b>The headliners will be you and me.</b>

12:10.000 --> 12:13.540
<b>If you keep behaving like 
you're my little brother...</b>

12:15.510 --> 12:19.180
<b>...you will never surpass me.</b>

12:20.170 --> 12:22.730
<b><i>Just you watch, 
you bad excuse for a big brother.</i></b>

12:23.680 --> 12:25.300
<b><i>I'm going to...</i></b>

12:28.360 --> 12:33.060
<b>"My dream for the future is to become 
a soccer player like my big brother."</b>

12:34.040 --> 12:36.020
<b>"Big Bro will be the best striker,</b>

12:36.360 --> 12:41.810
<b>and I'll be the second-best striker 
in the world. We'll win the World Cup."</b>

12:42.560 --> 12:44.490
<b>Man, these Itoshi brothers...</b>

12:44.490 --> 12:46.030
<b>They're monsters.</b>

12:46.030 --> 12:48.550
<b>The line of that shot 
wasn't tight enough, Rin.</b>

12:48.550 --> 12:50.740
<b>Really? I'll be more careful next time.</b>

12:50.990 --> 12:53.750
<b>Can you pick up the tempo a little bit?</b>

12:53.750 --> 12:56.210
<b>Sure. I'll try.</b>

12:57.250 --> 12:59.670
<b><i>It's fun playing soccer with my big bro.</i></b>

13:00.180 --> 13:03.130
<b><i>With my big bro, I can become invincible.</i></b>

13:05.330 --> 13:07.550
<b><i>I'll become the best in 
the world with my big bro.</i></b>

13:07.640 --> 13:08.760
<b>All right!</b>

13:11.240 --> 13:12.470
<b>You
Win</b>

13:12.470 --> 13:14.560
<b>Ugh, I won.</b>

13:14.560 --> 13:17.000
<b>You wasted your luck, Rin.</b>

13:18.440 --> 13:20.650
<b>Destroying the evidence.</b>

13:22.870 --> 13:26.890
<b>Rin, what do you think about
when you play soccer?</b>

13:26.890 --> 13:29.120
<b>Huh? Nothing really.</b>

13:29.670 --> 13:31.840
<b>I just think about scoring, I guess.</b>

13:32.180 --> 13:35.830
<b>I know you'll pass the ball to me
 if I run into a hot spot.</b>

13:36.330 --> 13:38.000
<b>What do you mean by a "hot spot"?</b>

13:38.280 --> 13:42.960
<b>Um... Those places where 
the enemy panics and breaks down.</b>

13:45.690 --> 13:48.830
<b>You rely on your gut too much.</b>

13:48.830 --> 13:51.930
<b>But you pass the ball to me, 
so it's all good, right?</b>

13:51.930 --> 13:54.890
<b>Playing with other guys 
just doesn't feel satisfying.</b>

13:55.360 --> 13:58.600
<b>What are you gonna do 
when I'm not around?</b>

13:58.600 --> 14:02.190
<b>I don't know, but I guess 
I'll find a replacement.</b>

14:02.190 --> 14:04.530
<b>As if you could replace me.</b>

14:04.530 --> 14:06.200
<b>Who do you think I am?</b>

14:06.200 --> 14:07.070
<b>Ouch.</b>

14:07.330 --> 14:12.030
<b>Yeah, okay, fine, oh great Itoshi Sae,
 the best in the world.</b>

14:13.560 --> 14:16.840
<b>Rin. I'm leaving for Spain tomorrow.</b>

14:17.260 --> 14:21.380
<b>I'm going to be joining the academy of 
the best soccer club in the world, Royale.</b>

14:22.000 --> 14:23.750
<b>Why so formal all of a sudden?</b>

14:24.070 --> 14:25.090
<b>I know that.</b>

14:25.780 --> 14:28.800
<b>You're going to be the 
best striker in the world, right?</b>

14:29.130 --> 14:32.430
<b>I'm just going there before you. 
You'd better catch up soon.</b>

14:33.900 --> 14:36.980
<b>While I'm gone, don't you dare give up.</b>

14:37.480 --> 14:38.460
<b>Right.</b>

14:38.920 --> 14:43.440
<b>For now, my goal is to be the best 
in Japan and get scouted like you.</b>

14:43.440 --> 14:45.890
<b>Yeah. Then onto the world stage.</b>

14:46.360 --> 14:48.740
<b>We'll become the best in the world together.</b>

14:51.610 --> 14:53.370
<b><i>Honestly, I'm a little sad.</i></b>

14:54.330 --> 14:56.170
<b><i>But I'll make sure I catch up to him.</i></b>

14:56.830 --> 14:58.790
<b>Big Bro, take care.</b>

14:59.030 --> 15:00.370
<b>I'm off.</b>

15:00.370 --> 15:02.790
<b>To become the best striker in the world.</b>

15:04.790 --> 15:07.610
<b><i>Next time I see him, I want...</i></b>

15:09.210 --> 15:12.180
<b><i>to be someone who can 
fight on the world stage.</i></b>

15:13.280 --> 15:16.890
<b><i>Playing soccer without my big bro 
is confining and awkward, but...</i></b>

15:16.890 --> 15:17.850
<b>Pass it, Rin!</b>

15:17.850 --> 15:18.770
<b>Rin, over here!</b>

15:18.770 --> 15:19.770
<b>Gimme the ball!</b>

15:20.720 --> 15:22.990
<b><i>I need to ascend to my bro's level.</i></b>

15:23.710 --> 15:25.940
<b><i>Now that this team has lost my big bro,</i></b>

15:27.660 --> 15:31.780
<b><i>I'll make it the best in Japan in his place.</i></b>

15:34.760 --> 15:36.800
<b>Heya. Practicing late again?</b>

15:36.800 --> 15:37.530
<b>Yeah.</b>

15:37.530 --> 15:40.170
<b>It's freezing! I'm heading home, Rin.</b>

15:47.050 --> 15:49.110
<b>Oh. Snow.</b>

15:51.380 --> 15:54.340
<b>The line of that shot wasn't tight enough.</b>

15:54.650 --> 15:56.300
<b>Oh, Big Bro—</b>

16:02.420 --> 16:03.620
<b>Welcome home.</b>

16:04.530 --> 16:06.840
<b>Yeah. I'm back.</b>

16:08.330 --> 16:10.170
<b>I see you in the news all the time.</b>

16:10.680 --> 16:13.860
<b>You've played in Royale's 
academy games, scored goals...</b>

16:13.860 --> 16:15.490
